import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Privacy Policy – Teraport" lang="en" altHref="/de/datenschutz/">
  <article class="tp-container prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>1. Controller</h2>
    <p>
      Teraport GmbH<br />
      Kellerstr. 29, 81667 Munich, Germany<br />
      Represented by the managing director: Raphael Heilig<br />
      Phone: <a href="tel:+4989651086700">+49 (0)89 651086 700</a> ·
      E-mail: <a class="email" data-u="info" data-d="teraport.de">info(at)teraport.de</a>
    </p>

    <h2>2. Hosting and server log files</h2>
    <p>
      When you visit this website, the web server automatically processes technical access data
      (server log files): the IP address of the requesting device, date and time of access, the
      page or file requested, the amount of data transferred, the referrer URL, and browser type
      and operating system. This data is technically required to deliver the website and to
      ensure its stability and security (legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR). It is not combined
      with other data sources. Log files are deleted automatically after a short period.
    </p>
    <p>
      This website is hosted by: STRATO GmbH, Otto-Ostrowski-Straße 7, 10249 Berlin,
      Germany. A data processing agreement pursuant to Art. 28 GDPR is in place with the
      hosting provider.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Contacting us</h2>
    <p>
      If you contact us by e-mail or phone, we process the details you provide (e.g. name,
      e-mail address, content of your request) solely to handle your request (legal basis:
      Art. 6 (1) (b) GDPR where the request relates to a contract, otherwise Art. 6 (1) (f)
      GDPR). The data is deleted once it is no longer required to process your request and no
      statutory retention obligations apply.
    </p>

    <h2>4. No cookies, no tracking</h2>
    <p>
      This website does not set cookies, does not use analytics or advertising services, and
      does not embed content from third-party servers. Fonts, images and all other resources
      are delivered locally from our server. No profiling takes place.
    </p>

    <h2>5. External links</h2>
    <p>
      Our website contains links to external websites (e.g. product sites). When you visit
      those sites, the privacy policies of the respective operators apply.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You have the right to access (Art. 15 GDPR), rectification (Art. 16), erasure (Art. 17),
      restriction of processing (Art. 18), data portability (Art. 20), and to object to
      processing based on Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR (Art. 21). To exercise these rights, simply
      contact us using the details above.
    </p>
    <p>
      You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a data protection supervisory
      authority. The authority responsible for us is the Bavarian State Office for Data
      Protection Supervision (BayLDA), Promenade 18, 91522 Ansbach, Germany, www.lda.bayern.de.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Encryption</h2>
    <p>
      This website uses TLS encryption (indicated by the lock symbol and "https://" in your
      browser's address bar).
    </p>

    <p class="teaser">Last updated: July 2026</p>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
